OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777546977
OL,3,CBurglars subject pensioner to
OL,4,C'obscene' violence during break-in
OL,6,FAn 85-year-old man has been
OL,7,Fhospitalised following what police
OL,8,Fhave described as a "deplorable" and
OL,9,F"heartless" aggravated burglary at his
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,FThe incident occurred in the early
OL,13,Fhours of Wednesday, 29 April, in
OL,14,FHelmshore, Lancashire.
OL,16,FA group of unknown suspects broke into
OL,17,Fthe property on Moss Close through the
OL,18,Ffront door and used an "obscene" level
OL,19,Fof violence when confronted by the
OL,20,Fpensioner and homeowner.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777546977
OL,3,CBurglars subject pensioner to
OL,4,C'obscene' violence during break-in
OL,6,FAfter the attack, the offenders fled
OL,7,Fthe scene by smashing their way out of
OL,8,Fthe house through the conservatory.
OL,10,FThe victim was rushed to hospital
OL,11,Fsuffering from a head injury and cuts
OL,12,Fto his face. He remains there for
OL,13,Ftreatment.
OL,15,FPolice say his 86-year-old wife was
OL,16,Fphysically unharmed but she has been
OL,17,Fleft "deeply shocked" by the ordeal.
OL,19,FLancashire Police have launched an
OL,20,Finvestigation and are working to
OL,21,Fidentify those responsible.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777546977
OL,3,CBurglars subject pensioner to
OL,4,C'obscene' violence during break-in
OL,6,FOfficers confirmed that extensive
OL,7,Fdamage was caused to the property,
OL,8,Fthough it remains unclear at this
OL,9,Fstage if any items were stolen.
OL,11,FDetective Sergeant Stu Peall, of the
OL,12,Fburglary team, condemned the attack in
OL,13,Fa scathing statement: "This is a
OL,14,Fdeplorable offence, committed against
OL,15,Fan elderly couple in their own home.
OL,17,F"It's an utterly heartless, cowardly
OL,18,Fand despicable offence and we will
OL,19,Fleave no stone unturned in our efforts
OL,20,Fto find those responsible."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777546977
OL,3,CBurglars subject pensioner to
OL,4,C'obscene' violence during break-in
OL,6,FHe continued: "This couple can't have
OL,7,Fbeen a serious threat to anyone, the
OL,8,Flevel of violence used is obscene and
OL,9,FI appeal to anyone with knowledge of
OL,10,Fthe offence or the identity of the
OL,11,Foffenders to come forward."
OL,13,FEnquiries are ongoing, and detectives
OL,14,Fare urging anyone with information to
OL,15,Fcontact them`including individuals who
OL,16,Fmay operate on the "periphery of
OL,17,Fcrime."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777546977
OL,3,CBurglars subject pensioner to
OL,4,C'obscene' violence during break-in
OL,6,F"Even those in or on the periphery of
OL,7,Fcrime cannot surely condone this
OL,8,Fbehaviour," Det Sgt Peall added. "I
OL,9,Fwould appeal to them to do what is
OL,10,Fright and to come forward."
OL,12,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,13,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,14,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,15,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
